84
00:06:42,660 --> 00:06:45,660
Vaig fent, i no hi ha vessals.

85
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:48,660
El bo és que no hi ha ningú, no hi ha gossos,

86
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:50,660
