141
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:29,660
Vull dir que ara veig això i estic pensant en allò.

142
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:30,660
Val.

143
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:33,660
Ostres, ostres, que em caic.

144
