La pesada de les polaines.

153
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,660
Va, vinga, va.

154
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:02,660
Que em caic.

155
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,660
Val.

156
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:08,660
